{"body": "I'll stick with the same 2 cents here as well: \n\n```ruby\nperson.errors.unique_messages\n# vs\nperson.errors.each_with_object({}) { |(attr, errors), h| h[attr] = errors.to_sentence }\n\nperson.errors.unique_message(:address)\n# vs\nperson.errors[:address].to_sentence\n```\n\nI'd rather use the last one in any scenario I can think of (in my apps), and it also adds the possibility of giving arguments to `#to_sentence` if necessary. Again, that's just me and my thoughts ;)\n\nThanks for your contribution.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/7102293", "created_at": "2012-07-19T15:55:50Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7107#issuecomment-7102293", "updated_at": "2012-07-19T15:55:50Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7107, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ffc3bd3543c15100beb3